  "body": "# Problem\nWhen receiving a chat referral url (`https://join.status.im/u/chatkey?=invitecode`), the recipient can accept terms of the referral program to release a Starter Pack (and attribution to a referrer). Currently when the user taps Accept, there is no feedback confirming that a Starter Pack is released. As the transaction can take up to 30 min this can leave people confused about whether they will receive their Starter Pack.\n\n- Show Pending state as previously designed and now technically feasible\n- When tapping on `Pending` navigate to transaction history tab in wallet\ncc @errorists for your confirmation and other ideas\n\n![States](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/35233054/94826625-cddc9680-0407-11eb-94b2-60b6cf56daa2.png)\n\n### User story\n- As a new user being informed that I will receive a Starter Pack I want to receive feedback showing the state of this transaction\n- As a user I want to get more details on a pending transaction\n\n## Implementation\n\n\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n\n## Notes\n\n\n\n## Future Steps\n#11021",
